Package: arkansas.gov
Title: Arkansas GIS Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for Arkansas GIS open data (ArcGIS FeatureServer). Query boundaries, health, environment, and transportation layers.
